sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>8081/TCP health<br/>8443/TCP metrics
    participant Helm as HelmRenderer<br/>(in-process)
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-CA)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS verify-full
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>9000/443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Admin,S3: Flow 1: MLflow CR Reconciliation

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update MLflow CR<br/>(mlflow.opendatahub.io/v1)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (informer)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Operator->>Helm: Render embedded Helm chart<br/>(translate CR spec → values)
    Helm-->>Operator: Unstructured manifests<br/>(Deployment, Service, SA,<br/>NetworkPolicy, PVC, ServiceMonitor)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply manifests<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update HTTPRoute<br/>(parent ref: data-science-gateway)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ConsoleLink<br/>(OpenShift console menu)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update MLflow CR status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Status confirmed

    Note over Admin,S3: Flow 2: Client Request via Gateway API

    participant Client as External Client

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/...<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (K8s)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS (service-CA)<br/>Passthrough Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, Delegated Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allow/Deny
    alt Authorized
        MLflow->>PG: Query/Store metadata<br/>PostgreSQL/5432<br/>TLS verify-full, credentials
        PG-->>MLflow: Result set
        MLflow->>S3: Store/Retrieve artifacts<br/>HTTPS/9000 or 443<br/>TLS, AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data
        MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    else Denied
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over Admin,S3: Flow 3: CA Bundle Assembly (Pod Init)

    participant InitCA as combine-ca-bundles<br/>(init container)
    participant Watcher as ca-bundle-watcher<br/>(sidecar)

    InitCA->>InitCA: Read system CAs +<br/>odh-trusted-ca-bundle +<br/>custom CA ConfigMap
    InitCA->>InitCA: Concatenate → combined PEM<br/>(emptyDir: combined-ca-bundle)
    Note over InitCA: Init complete, pod starts

    loop Every 30 seconds
        Watcher->>Watcher: Poll ConfigMap volumes<br/>for changes
        alt CA bundle changed
            Watcher->>Watcher: Regenerate combined PEM<br/>(emptyDir: combined-ca-bundle)
            Note over MLflow: Picks up new CAs<br/>without pod restart
        end
    end
